title: Extra Cheesy Chermoula Chickpea-Stuffed Capsicum with Leafy Couscous & Garlic Yoghurt
description: If you’re as crazy about capsicums as we are then gather around and try out the latest capsicum creation - they’re stuffed full of saucy chickpeas beans sprinkled in Cheddar cheese to add a melted gooey layer on top. We’re these stuffed capsicum’s number one fans!
